  <bioghist id="aspace_fb964a4d258ef4df62b9c7a255911b48">
    <head>Historical Note</head>
<p>The United Federation of Teachers, a New York-based teachers union, was founded in 1960 with a merger of the Teachers Guild and the High School Teachers Association. George Altomare was a founding member and leader in the UFT.</p>  </bioghist>
  <custodhist id="aspace_623e23ab89df74f79addb4acb37f8a87">
    <head>Custodial History</head>
<p>The collection was donated by George Altomare in 1989. Altomare had created these recordings at United Federation Teacher events, but they were not owned by the UFT or a part of its records.</p>  </custodhist>
